			)
			(justify left bottom)
		)
	)
	(gr_text "T10000/T10K size box for 2.5'' HDD\nsize is not too far from the IBM Jaguar 3592\nv0.2\n"
		(at 48.1 73.4 0)
		(layer "Edge.Cuts")
		(uuid "d8d976c0-20ca-4112-93eb-b073f655d4a1")
		(effects
			(font
				(size 10 10)
				(thickness 1)
			)
			(justify left bottom)
		)
	)
	(gr_text "What is this crazy Idea to build that witch pcb?\n- because PCB industry build consistent, reproductible things with a known pipeline\n- because it's easy to be ul94\n- because soldier is better than glue, you can dis-assemble, re-assemble (use a pump to un-glue ;)\n- giving the SDL of a plastic injection mold, won't really help people\n- 3D printing does not compete, AFAIK for ul94, reproductibily, even cost, let me know"
		(at 41.35 560.85 0)
		(layer "Edge.Cuts")
		(uuid "dc5f5306-f190-468c-a260-15d57997e438")
		(effects
			(font
				(size 3 3)
				(thickness 0.4)
			)
			(justify left bottom)
		)
